== Hindi ==

=== Pronunciation ===
/a/ short or long [[schwa]]: as the a in above or ago

=== Letter ===

First letter and first vowel of the [[Devanagari]] script. Besides the initial position in a word, the letter is not written, instead it is assumed in the form of the consonant characters unless another vowel matra is used or a diacritic mark, the [[virama]], removes it.

